window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Humanity is defeated.</p> <p>Ten years ago the Sythians invaded the galaxy with one goal: to wipe out the human race.</p> <p>They are hiding.</p> <p>Now the survivors are hiding in the last human sector of the galaxy: Dark Space--once a place of exile for criminals, now the last refuge of mankind.</p> <p>They are isolated.</p> <p>The once galaxy-spanning Imperium of Star Systems is left guarding the gate which is the only way in or out of Dark Space--but not everyone is satisfied with their governance.</p>"; 
